    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The college library is really good for students who are hostelite",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some of staff will really help you regarding your problems or even what to do next",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Tech Culture is good for CS Major, like you will get the senior support for the update regarding new tech event and to support the junior for new skills learning and trends going on.",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The thing I like about college is there is environment for the students who are willing to do something and are trying hard to get some skills.",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has a dedicated placement cell which organized a various company drives for placing the students. The College TPO is very helpful. In our batch, the percentage of placed student is around 60-70%.",
          "name": "Pratik Rane",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty of each department is highly qualified and some have industry experience.Some Professor employ the innovative teaching method including practical demonstrations.",
          "name": "Pratik Rane",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college also contains a gym and a canteen. The College also have parking at backside of college.",
          "name": "Pratik Rane",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college have modern infrastructure with well equipped laboratories,libraries and classrooms. The Campus amenities like sports facilities in which a cricket ground, volleyball ground, basketball ground, kabaddi ground, badminton ground.",
          "name": "Pratik Rane",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The fee is too much for course not everyone can afford that much amount of fee",
          "name": "Shantanu Sunil Gaikwad",
          "course_tag_name": "MBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sometimes lectures seems like boring but we cant bunk.",
          "name": "Ajay Patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There No big canteen for students only has cafe and one more thing (college shuru hote hi khtm ho jata hai)",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college Campus is so small there are only 2 building ( in which only one has lift )for all engineering branches and the ground is very dusty and small",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teaching faculty focus more on syllabus rather than actual skills",
          "name": "Rutik patil",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The range of Core companies for the placement can be expanded.",
          "name": "Pratik Rane",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The ceiling of building need maintenance.",
          "name": "Pratik Rane",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "SPPU, Pune"
    }
